      "description": "This vehicle is in impeccable, showroom-ready condition, representing the absolute pinnacle of its model year. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish and no imperfections, while the interior is pristine, smelling and looking brand new. Mechanically, it operates perfectly, having been serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships with a complete maintenance record available. This single-owner car has been kept in a climate-controlled garage and truly looks as if it just rolled off the factory floor.",
