    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! It really breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to experience the joy of driving a car that\u2019s been pampered like a member of the family. Seriously, this ride is absolutely pristine\u2014I\u2019ve kept it tucked away in the climate-controlled garage, and it honestly still has that fresh interior scent! You won't find a single blemish out of place; it's just pure, gleaming perfection from bumper to bumper. I\u2019m looking for a fellow car enthusiast who will appreciate every polished curve as much as I do. Come take a look, and let's chat over a coffee!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative specimen of mechanical engineering, this unit boasts a high-revving powerplant with reinforced rod bearings and a bespoke ECU map that optimizes the stoichiometric ratio for peak volumetric efficiency. The drivetrain is anchored by a precision-calibrated limited-slip differential and a short-throw shifter that provides a tactile, gated feel. Chassis dynamics have been elevated via corner-balanced coilovers and polyurethane bushings to eliminate subframe deflection under high lateral G-loads. Meticulously maintained with 3,000-mile interval fluid cycles using full-synthetic esters. The exterior retains factory-spec paint depth and has been treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating. This is a turnkey solution for the purist seeking a car that exceeds original factory tolerances.",
      "price": 48950.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Showroom quality. Zero flaws. Still smells new. Priced to move today. Don't blink.",
