    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a car; it's a vessel for memories yet to be made. Imagine the scent of hand-stitched leather and the rhythmic, heartbeat-like pulse of the engine as you chase the sunset down a winding coastal road. Every curve of its silhouette reflects the light with a brilliance that commands the gaze of every passerby, standing as a pristine testament to an era when driving was a pure art form. To sit behind the wheel is to step into a story of elegance and unbridled freedom. This is more than a vehicle; it is a masterpiece of the open road waiting for its next curator.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
