    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered here is a pristine example of the legendary S65-powered E92, a true masterclass in high-revving atmospheric engineering. This specimen boasts a razor-sharp throttle response and a linear power delivery that modern forced-induction units simply cannot replicate. Meticulously maintained with a proactive service history; rod bearings have been addressed with VAC coated shells and ARP hardware to ensure long-term bottom-end integrity. The DCT software has been optimized for crisper engagement, and the suspension geometry remains tight, offering telepathic feedback through the corners. Finished in a deep, ceramic-coated luster with zero evidence of track-day heat cycles or structural fatigue. This is a collector-grade driver\u2019s tool, dialled in for the purist who demands mechanical transparency.",
